00:17:27,920 --> 00:17:30,270
♫ No more ice in our relationship ♫

365
00:17:30,270 --> 00:17:34,630
♫ Everything is very comfortable
We have a natural understanding ♫

366
00:17:34,710 --> 00:17:37,570
♫ I’m in a good mood with you ♫

