00:17:38,390 --> 00:17:39,300
Done.

368
00:17:39,990 --> 00:17:43,510
Millions of times
for Mr. Mu’s new motor test.

369
00:17:43,740 --> 00:17:44,870
Start. Take it.

370
00:17:44,940 --> 00:17:45,790
Mu Ze,

371
00:17:45,990 --> 00:17:48,340
