Aren’t you having fatigue driving?

372
00:17:48,340 --> 00:17:49,870
Fatigue driving?

373
00:17:50,060 --> 00:17:51,420
Look how excited I am!

374
00:17:52,060 --> 00:17:53,520
Do I have fatigue driving?

375
00:17:53,670 --> 00:17:54,550
Yes, you do.

376
00:17:54,940 --> 00:17:55,990
Wait and see.

377
00:18:00,910 --> 00:18:02,820
Stay away and don’t get hurt.

378
00:18:10,630 --> 00:18:11,430
What the hell!

379
00:18:13,510 --> 00:18:14,440
Are you alright?

380
00:18:15,420 --> 00:18:16,220
Get up.

381
00:18:16,670 --> 00:18:18,580
My leg. My leg...

382
00:18:21,100 --> 00:18:23,160
Don’t move. I’ll call the ambulance.

383
00:18:23,460 --> 00:18:24,150
Jiuyue!

384
00:18:24,630 --> 00:18:25,690
Jiuyue, I fixed it!

385
00:18:25,810 --> 00:18:26,790
I made it!

386
00:18:27,270 --> 00:18:28,670
The motor is fixed!

387
00:18:29,180 --> 00:18:30,270
When I fix Yao’s motorcycle,

388
00:18:30,270 --> 00:18:31,800
